    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📱SMS Outreach Executor\n\n**Purpose**\nSends short personalized SMS messages to leads via Twilio. SMS is the second touch in the outreach sequence — only fires after email with no reply.\n\n**How it works**\nRuns every **2 hours** → finds leads where email was sent 3+ days ago with no reply → personalizes the AI-generated SMS → sends via Twilio API → logs activity → updates lead status.\n\n**Key Rules**\n- Only fires if email was sent **3+ days ago**\n- All messages include **\"Reply STOP to opt-out\"** (required by law)\n- Max **160 characters** per SMS\n- Uses `TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER` from environment",
